MATT RODBARD: Doenjang and miso.

00:30:27.773 --> 00:30:30.720
DEUKI HONG: So don't say
doenjang is Korean miso.

00:30:30.720 --> 00:30:32.740
MATT RODBARD: Please
don't say that.

00:30:32.740 --> 00:30:33.940
They're very different.

00:30:33.940 --> 00:30:35.772
DEUKI HONG: It's very different.

00:30:35.772 --> 00:30:37.480
MATT RODBARD: Maybe
