individual in their life

00:32:44.690 --> 00:32:46.310
who tells them where to go.

00:32:46.310 --> 00:32:47.399
And it's wonderful.

00:32:47.399 --> 00:32:48.940
DEUKI HONG: You have
one, that Matty.

00:32:48.940 --> 00:32:51.660
MATT RODBARD: I have one
here and another one--

