a science behind that.

00:50:10.321 --> 00:50:11.600
You guys are smart.

00:50:11.600 --> 00:50:13.770
Y'all look it up somewhere.

00:50:13.770 --> 00:50:14.450
But we do.

00:50:14.450 --> 00:50:17.320
And it's a big part
of our culture.

00:50:17.320 --> 00:50:19.140
HILLARY: I know our
time is winding down,

00:50:19.140 --> 00:50:21.182
so I have some lightning
round questions for you.

00:50:21.182 --> 00:50:22.723
So I'm going to ask
them fast, you're

00:50:22.723 --> 00:50:23.812
going to answer them fast.

00:50:23.812 --> 00:50:25.230
MATT RODBARD: Okay.

00:50:25.230 --> 00:50:27.270
HILLARY: For novice
and beginner cooks,

00:50:27.270 --> 00:50:29.182
where should they
start in your cookbook.

