bean paste soup.

00:50:32.890 --> 00:50:34.360
DEUKI HONG: Make
the quick kimchis.

00:50:34.360 --> 00:50:35.526
MATT RODBARD: Quick kimchis?

00:50:35.526 --> 00:50:36.360
DEUKI HONG: Yeah.

00:50:36.360 --> 00:50:39.020
HILLARY: And for those
who are just less familiar

00:50:39.020 --> 00:50:40.950
with Korean food in
general, how would

00:50:40.950 --> 00:50:44.475
you suggest they approach
a Korean restaurant menu?

00:50:44.475 --> 00:50:46.350
MATT RODBARD: For me,
ask a lot of questions.

00:50:46.350 --> 00:50:49.184
You just go in and go in with
maybe a little bit of a plan

00:50:49.184 --> 00:50:50.600
but like I'm going
to have a soup,

00:50:50.600 --> 00:50:51.975
I'm going to have
a barbecue, I'm

00:50:51.975 --> 00:50:53.410
going to have maybe a pancake.

00:50:53.410 --> 00:50:54.575
But start asking questions.

00:50:54.575 --> 00:50:56.290
It's so important.

00:50:56.290 --> 00:50:58.165
DEUKI HONG: I don't
think you're going to get

00:50:58.165 --> 00:50:59.350
any answers from a Korean.

00:50:59.350 --> 00:50:59.849
Whatever.

00:50:59.849 --> 00:51:01.482
I mean, pick something.

00:51:01.482 --> 00:51:02.835
Hopefully it tastes good.

00:51:02.835 --> 00:51:04.080
Roll a dice.

00:51:04.080 --> 00:51:05.660
What do you want me to say?

00:51:05.660 --> 00:51:07.820
HILLARY: Do you have
any recommendations

00:51:07.820 --> 00:51:10.550
for good Korean food in San
Francisco or is the answer

00:51:10.550 --> 00:51:11.930
get on a plane and go to LA?

00:51:11.930 --> 00:51:16.530
MATT RODBARD: It's a very--
San Francisco doesn't

00:51:16.530 --> 00:51:19.180
have an abundance of
Korean restaurants compared

00:51:19.180 --> 00:51:21.400
to other cities,
like Los Angeles.

00:51:21.400 --> 00:51:23.340
But honestly--

00:51:23.340 --> 00:51:25.130
DEUKI HONG: Sorry,
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:51:25.130 --> 00:51:27.820
MATT RODBARD: So I interviewed
in the book, I went to--

00:51:27.820 --> 00:51:30.550
AUDIENCE: When are you
going to open up one here?

00:51:30.550 --> 00:51:32.040
MATT RODBARD: This crowd wow.

