00:56:21.800 --> 00:56:22.860
MATT RODBARD: Done
by Bourdain Books,

00:56:22.860 --> 00:56:24.420
Matt Goulding's the author.

00:56:24.420 --> 00:56:25.350
Highly recommend it.

00:56:25.350 --> 00:56:27.506
It's fantastic.

00:56:27.506 --> 00:56:29.590
HILLARY: I had a very
flippant thought which

00:56:29.590 --> 00:56:32.590
