is that both are better in LA

00:56:36.040 --> 00:56:38.552
than in almost any
other location.

00:56:38.552 --> 00:56:40.260
Literally almost any
other American city.

00:56:40.260 --> 00:56:41.250
DEUKI HONG: SF is good.

00:56:41.250 --> 00:56:44.690
MATT RODBARD: Yeah
it is really good.

00:56:44.690 --> 00:56:49.650
HILLARY: It's just, Los Angeles
as a culinary powerhouse

00:56:49.650 --> 00:56:54.690
in our country has a few really
niche areas where they just

00:56:54.690 --> 00:56:55.380
really excel.

00:56:55.380 --> 00:56:58.887
And Japanese food
in LA is incredible.

